Re-imagined in always novel ways, the emblematic Prada triangle logo is turned into a knit patch. The Fall Winter 2020 collection presents synchronous yet antonymic points of view on tradition, in a mix of linear and voluminous silhouettes that portrays the identities of the modern man.
